night life of the gods ( also known as thorne smith 's night life of the gods ) is a 1935 american fantasy film released by universal pictures . based on a 1931 novel by thorne smith , the film was directed by lowell sherman and starred alan mowbray as a scientist who devises a ray that can turn people to stone and bring statues to life . for many years believed to be a lost film , a 35 mm print surfaced in the 1980s in a donation to the ucla film and television archive .